仆街」照片一開始在泰國也很風行，[名人](http://www.bangkokpost.com/print/242899/
"http://www.bangkokpost.com/print/242899/")、[抗議民眾](http://suthichaiyoon.blogspot.com/2011/06/red-
shirts-go-planking-at-ratchaprasong.html
"http://suthichaiyoon.blogspot.com/2011/06/red-shirts-go-planking-at-
ratchaprasong.html")、[政治人物](http://www.bangkokpost.com/breakingnews/242741/chuwit-
pulls-off-a-plank "http://www.bangkokpost.com/breakingnews/242741/chuwit-
pulls-off-a-
plank")紛紛公布自己的仆街照片；Faceebook[頁面](http://www.facebook.com/bkkplank?sk=wall
"http://www.facebook.com/bkkplank?sk=wall")「曼谷仆街社群」也隨之成立，讓一般民眾上傳自己在各種奇異場所的仆街照片。

[![](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2011/06/planking-375x280.jpg)](http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1763526369187&set=o.213766261988283&type=1&ref=nf)

照片來自Facebook頁面Princess OftheMoon YathAkira

以下這張仆街照片的主角身穿袈裟，在網路上引起熱烈討論，甚至有人懸賞獎金，要找出照片中的這個人。

[![](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2011/06/monk-375x281.jpg)](http://yfrog.com/gy9o0jzj)

照片來自yfrog頁面CrimeWatchCH

「[文化觀察中心](http://www.nationmultimedia.com/2011/06/21/national/Nude-planking-
photos-online-an-offence-30158300.html
"http://www.nationmultimedia.com/2011/06/21/national/Nude-planking-photos-
online-an-offence-30158300.html")」強調裸體仆街照片「失禮」，但Saksith
Saiyasombut[反對](http://asiancorrespondent.com/57921/thailands-cultural-
heralds-to-crackdown-on-planking/
"http://asiancorrespondent.com/57921/thailands-cultural-heralds-to-crackdown-
on-planking/")這種言論：

> 又是種「失禮」行為，仆街照片當然是沒什麼正面功能，只是種無意義的趣味，搏君一笑罷了。
>
>
> 這些人士自詡為「文化先驅」，沒有靜靜看著熱潮退去（當今網路風潮來去都快），反而小題大作，下回各位若要成為良好典範，請不要一切訴諸直覺反應，只想著要保護所謂的「合禮行為」，一笑置之即可！

仆街照片熱潮很快就由「跪坐照」（[Pub Peab](http://www.cnngo.com/bangkok/play/thailand-
embraces-planking-and-gives-it-twist-592652
"http://www.cnngo.com/bangkok/play/thailand-embraces-planking-and-gives-it-
twist-592652")）取而代之，心態大同小異，只是增添了泰國文化色彩。

[![](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/pub-peab-
monk-375x250.jpg)](http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=238796602801067&set=o.111894685567117&type=1&ref=nf)

相關Facebook[頁面](http://www.facebook.com/pubpeab
"http://www.facebook.com/pubpeab")已有至少200,339人支持，也設有[Twitter帳號](http://twitter.com/#%21/Pubpeab_Th
"http://twitter.com/#!/Pubpeab_Th")。

[![](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2011/06/pub_twitter-375x181.png)](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2011/06/pub_twitter.png)

就連官方也[支持](http://www.nationmultimedia.com/2011/06/21/national/Planking-with-a-
Thai-slant-30158356.html
"http://www.nationmultimedia.com/2011/06/21/national/Planking-with-a-Thai-
slant-30158356.html")「跪坐照」，認為有助推廣泰國文化。

[![](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/pub-
peab-375x281.jpg)](http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=235203683162902&set=o.111894685567117&type=1&ref=nf)

